item.title: Bonus: Behind The Bastard Lord
item.description:
Merry Christmas, happy Kwanzaa, and a cozy Yule! (Hanukkah was already almost a month ago)

As a warm thanks we decided to share this month's Underground Mythos with you all here. It's a Mythos-themed parody of the fantastic podcast Behind The Bastards.

"A poor Robert Evans impersonation is joined by M Starr Brannigan to talk about a particularly toothy bastard as well as a bevy of other bastards along the way... Feed: https://anchor.fm/s/4c3e9ecc/podcast/rss
